content:
Hi there! <#1267941954243526756> 
Qu. Does anyone  know if the Harris-Walz Campaign can would mail me a few Harris posters to incentivize the attendees at my event to donate and help get out the vote?

The official campaign shop is really backed up with order fulfillment. It might be better to reach out to the field office closest to you. They should be able to get you signs quicker.  I can help you find your local office
You can ask in <#1245826306780823563> , but I only know of the swag for hosts (not for guests).

<@791857656897732648> What kind of swag for host? I am hosting a Debate Watch  Party, I will host an election Party.  I will take whatever.

Thank you so much.
<@568257600228032512> The local office would be a long shot...
